\\begin{theorem}[Efron-Stein]
Let X_1, ..., X_n be independent random variables and f in L^2.
Then
\\[
\\mathrm{Var}(f(X)) \\le \\sum_{i=1}^n \\mathbb{E}[\\mathrm{Var}(f(X) \\mid G_i^{\\mathrm{except}})].
\\]
\\end{theorem}

\\begin{proof}
Use martingale telescoping decomposition and Jensen inequality.
\\end{proof}
